data.description: Welcome to 708 James Lee Rd, a stunning Fort Walton Beach gem that combines modern elegance with comfortable living.  Step inside and be greeted by the timeless allure of vinyl floors throughout the entire home.  The spacious living area flows seamlessly into the kitchen, where you will find granite countertops that not only enhance the aesthetic appeal but also offer ample workspace for culinary endeavors.  Equipped with stainless steel appliances, the kitchen is a chef's dream come true.  All popcorn ceilings have been removed, leaving you with a clean, contemporary canvas to personalize.  The master suite is your oasis of tranquility, complete with a luxurious walk in shower.  Enjoy the screened porch equipped with heating and cooling.  Don't miss the opportunity to see this home!
